      "text": [
        " قَالَ رَسُولُ اَللَّهِ صَلَّى اَللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَ آلِهِ : \"مَا بُنِيَ بِنَاءٌ فِي اَلْإِسْلاَمِ أَحَبُّ إِلَى اَللَّهِ تَعَالَى مِنَ اَلتَّزْوِيجِ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4343 - Abdullah ibn al-Hakam narrated from Abu Ja'far Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as) that the Messenger of Allah (swt) (peace be upon him and his family) said:\n\"No structure in Islam is more beloved to Allah (swt), the Exalted, than marriage.\""
        ]
      }
